ory of gravitation which\nhas the full general invariance but has less physical degrees of freedom.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Feb 2007 07:40:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 9 Nov 2007 13:32:27 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 4 Jul 2008 10:23:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-09"}
